Spain’s PP Plans to Find Manager For Loterias, Expansion Reports

-- B y   C h a r l e s   P e n t y
-- 
2011-10-03T06:30:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/spain-s-pp-plans-to-find-manager-for-loterias-expansion-reports.html
Spain ’s  People’s Party  is studying
placing the management of the state lottery company in private
hands while maintaining the government’s ownership of it if it
wins November elections, Expansion reported, citing people
familiar with the situation it didn’t identify by name.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
